questions.questionText:
What is the computed width of the container in each scenario?

```css
.container {
  width: min(100%, 800px);
}
/* Scenario A: parent width = 1200px */
/* Scenario B: parent width = 400px */
```

What does this CSS produce?

```css
.hero {
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  /* Viewport is 375px wide */
}
```
